ot only is this a profitable experience, it can be fun too.<br><br>So, to all you level 5-12s, do this quest, have some fun and get some good armor!<br><br>Good Luck, I hope you liked my little experience with this quest, and even better experiences will happen to you!<br><br>-Boombaa Shadowslayer<br>11KPP of Items gaven away on the Innoruuk Server in 3 months, and is proud of it.</p>&nbsp;<br><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br>Boombaa Shadowslayer<br>51st Ogre Warrior<br><br>Hierophantt<br>10th Iksar Monk<br><br>Tenamin<br>10th Half Elf Pa</td></tr>
